node.text: Guys!  This is the first of three Valentine’s Weekend surprises.  First, I’m psyched to share that I’ll be at the TIFF Next Wave Film Festival this Saturday for a free live chat - and I’m bringing my short film Night Shifts with me! Head over to @TIFF_NET for more details - and stand by for moarrrrr 🤘❤️🤘
